msgctxt "mn1:171.1"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatopi, bhikkhave, arahaṃ sammāsambuddho pathaviṃ pathavito abhijānāti;"
msgstr ""
"The Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha directly "
"knows earth as earth."

msgctxt "mn1:171.2"
msgid ""
"pathaviṃ pathavito abhiññāya pathaviṃ na maññati, pathaviyā na maññati, "
